It appears that I am receiving only the phrase "Execution result:" without any additional context or details. Unfortunately, this makes it impossible for me to assist you with your interactions in the Factorio REPL environment.

2. **Execution Results**: Include any outputs, error messages, or relevant feedback that resulted from running that code.

Your cooperation in providing this information is essential for understanding your challenges and enabling me to offer meaningful assistance. Thank you!
